query:
SELECT 
  COUNT(*) as total_products,
  COUNT(detailedDescription) as has_detailed_desc,
  COUNT(specifications) as has_specifications,
  COUNT(particleSize) as has_particle_size,
  COUNT(poreSize) as has_pore_size,
  COUNT(columnLength) as has_column_length,
  COUNT(innerDiameter) as has_inner_diameter,
  COUNT(imageUrl) as has_image
FROM products
